The '''Gargan family''' was an [[Askajian/Legends|Askajian]] family from [[Askaji/Legends|Askaj]]. Members of this family had the middle name, '''d'al''''. The family was captured and sold to [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]]. Members of this family were [[Nautag d'al' Gargan|Nautag]] and [[Yarna d'al' Gargan/Legends|Yarna d'al' Gargan]] and their cubs, [[Luka d'al' Gargan|Luka]], [[Leia d'al' Gargan|Leia]] and [[Nautag d'al' Gargan II|Nautag (II)]].

